Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭 我又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃什麼點心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃巧克力類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上快到了 衝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 宮姐 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 宮姐 宮姐 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.75,Upper,,0,0,0,,日向 姐姐要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 妳醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐醒了 我們下樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太讚了 大家好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妳沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.48,Default,,600,0,0,,從很多意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.78,Default,,600,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:12.70,Default,,600,0,0,,很多意義上？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,600,0,,夏音 這樣更帥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,600,0,,小依 不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 今天也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 宮姐姐又只看小花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,1100,0,,是啊 乃愛也超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 妳回一下頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,太可愛啦 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也拍到好照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃什麼點心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 好吃程度僅次於妳做的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好像花的髮夾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,花的衣服雖然很土 但是髮卡很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是誰送的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 小時候外婆送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我一直很珍惜它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳外婆住在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,坐電車要兩個小時的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,附近有山 還有條漂亮的河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我每年都去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒見英國的外婆了 我還想看外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是妳的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,反正外婆基本都會誇人可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想在這種山裡河邊和大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不住下來的話很難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也是一次練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼的練習？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將來會去修學旅行對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以當作練習旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 練習旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我來當領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地呢 妳們想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒去過日本的這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想去這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那不如就去我外婆家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好 大家一起去花的外婆家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 真的要去嗎 我也去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大家都去的話會給人家添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我問一下媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉能輕鬆入選我最喜歡的日本的十種東西 是傳說級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,偶爾去溫泉放鬆一下的確不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉的話 我媽媽家附近有個不錯的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧 來個閨蜜會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,閨蜜會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去外婆家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,練習旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我問一下 妳稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆說我們可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒說我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,來嘛 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我又不擅長旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起去很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦 我去就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,宮子一起的話就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 宮小姐和孩子們關係特別要好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是只有宮子的話 來回路上還是不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不如這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對 去小花的外婆家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,打算大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來回路上我們也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來回路上是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去附近的溫泉旅館住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,正好我們在聊想三個人一起去溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小花外婆也說讓我們去放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就是這樣 再見啦 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽同意我去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我家也同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就大家一起去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要去旅行啦 好期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 我幫妳做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次和朋友一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好想趕快去啊 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 宮子看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我和宮子在一起也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 明天的準備做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 開始裝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 這個 還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有這個就不怕在山裡遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是去小花外婆家 不會遇難的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那個就別帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是旅行手冊 我打算和妳一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,手冊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 她叫宮子 是個特別擅長做點心的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她和小花她們特別要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 來一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我必須把這個做完 妳自己洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不快點睡覺的話 明天要起不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 妳怎麼會唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因為妳總是在唱啊 我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 妳聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道小花外婆家是個什麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和日向一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和乃愛一起的話去哪裡都開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛 怎麼了 泡暈了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種地方撩人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊 乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在這次旅行中要和日向拉近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要戴上這個去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面弄丟了我會後悔一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次和朋友一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好想趕快去啊 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,花 今天也穿鬍子哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是出門用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看不出有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 妳帶了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,遇難就不好了 我拿了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看 果然需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好 出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,難得來了 要不要走著去家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,反正妳缺乏運動 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,距離不是很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意 要走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是小花外婆家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,話說我還是第一次住在陌生人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要是個可怕的外婆該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,200,0,,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.39,Default,,200,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這次給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我很期待妳們的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,花 那件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,果然穿搭就得這樣
Comment: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的是衣服的(穿搭,coordinate)和(就得這樣,kodeneto)的諧音冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的是衣服的穿搭和就得這樣的諧音冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(890,973)}coordinate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(1075,973)}kodeneto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,穿搭就得這樣 真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,日本笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.03,Upper,,0,0,0,,我媽媽從以前就喜歡講冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆像是個有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,妳真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有我跟著宮姐 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題啦 妳去溫泉放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 孩子們就交給我 妳們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 後天中午我來接妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛 好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽也好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟房子很老了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,帶大家去二層吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好寬敞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說外婆搬過來之前是間旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好寬敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好寬敞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去探險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意 有點心吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼 開派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 難得大家來了 開個歡迎派對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 果然誇人可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有這麼多吃的 什麼時候遇難都不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想遇難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆 妳也和小花一樣喜歡點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每一種都很好吃 是妳親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 都是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆學會做點心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐也特別擅長做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.05,Upper,,0,0,0,,也不能說擅長 我只是喜歡做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 吃完點心就出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,旅行手冊 我和夏音一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們查了一下有趣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是班長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我這個領隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說要去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 有人拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,來 換上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是遇難時用的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我想遇難了也可以用上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想 感覺冷的時候有這個穿不就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 確實放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 一點也不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐 這件好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿哪件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來 這件給日向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那件給乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,小依和夏音穿這件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 來換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 妳不穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 大家穿著超合適
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿著這個在街上走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是個只要申請了就可以在外面Cosplay攝影的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來不想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這裡感覺可以 甚至可以說想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道一個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跟著我這個領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好讚啊 再登高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這是和日向拉近距離的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我上不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 我上不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 好讚啊 稍微抬起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 這不就跟平時做的事沒什麼區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒好棒 接下來擺一個回頭的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在辦什麼活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是修學旅行的練習旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有租衣服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好像宮姐做的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這種店
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐也來穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 宮姐也穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐穿著一定很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 一定很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妳打算只讓我們穿成這樣在街上走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,戀愛神籤？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我抽一個試試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓喜歡的人餵妳好吃的東西能拉近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛 有什麼好東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,久…久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好帥啊 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,穿…穿著這個走好羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳有資格說這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很適合妳 宮姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.84,0:24:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 接下來去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來…去摘葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,據說很甜很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是甜的什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要摘好多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吃多少摘多少
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,拿回去當禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不摘葡萄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 看我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.70,0:24:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我給妳拍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.83,0:24:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 難得穿上這麼漂亮的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.64,0:24:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 我也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不如拍張合影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.64,0:24:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有拍合影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.02,0:25:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 來拍張合影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.23,0:25:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拍不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.95,0:25:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候找別人幫忙就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.12,0:25:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍囉 來 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.96,0:25:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.29,0:25:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.71,0:25:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,回來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.17,0:25:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.34,0:25:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,町婆婆 妳來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.60,0:25:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我和小櫻喝茶聊天來著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.27,0:25:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這是外婆的朋友 町婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.11,0:25:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,妳…妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.57,0:25:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.57,0:25:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是 妳們為什麼穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.28,0:25:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.95,0:25:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:25:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是宮姐做的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.50,0:26:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 妳做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.75,0:26:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我愛好做衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人頭疼的愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.79,0:26:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 小花
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.42,0:26:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妳能否認嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.13,0:26:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.43,0:26:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.01,0:26:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.23,0:26:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起摘的 雖然因為小花偷吃已經少了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.69,0:26:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很好吃 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.53,0:26:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.49,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待外婆做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.42,0:26:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.83,0:26:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多菜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.25,0:26:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.30,0:26:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.76,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這些都是外婆做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.01,0:26:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.59,0:26:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來 妳們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:26:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 開吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.98,0:27:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.48,0:27:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.11,0:27:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.86,0:27:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,日向面前的炸雞塊 看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.91,0:27:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.00,0:27:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.34,0:27:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也吃炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.05,0:27:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐做的飯當然好吃 外婆做的飯也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.10,0:27:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多菜 我一個人可做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.18,0:27:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家覺得味噌湯味道怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.35,0:27:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,神的味噌湯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,神的味噌湯 神的味噌湯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.82,0:27:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只有神知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.57,0:27:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Comment: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,味噌的味道是(神之味噌湯,misoshiru)和(只有神知道,mizoshiru)的諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,味噌的味道是神之味噌湯和只有神知道的諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(890,973)}misoshiru
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(1167,973)}mizoshiru
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.45,0:28:03.87,Upper,,0,0,0,,日本笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.21,0:28:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不是很懂 但是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.08,0:28:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.75,0:28:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 今天妳們去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.42,0:28:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在河裡被沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.13,0:28:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.09,0:28:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,順流而下的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.89,0:28:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去玩泛舟了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.56,0:28:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.68,0:28:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,超好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有衝擊力
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.39,0:28:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.39,0:28:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然後去了岩疊 那之後去摘了葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.31,0:28:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 妳們帶回來的葡萄就當餐後甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.40,0:28:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,葡萄要不要來一粒？
Comment: 0,0:28:40.32,0:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(葡萄要不要來一粒,budo hitotsu budo)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.16,0:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,葡萄要不要來一粒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.16,0:28:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37\pos(960,973)}budo hitotsu budo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.91,0:28:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,諧音冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.17,0:28:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天不想再吃葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟小花偷吃了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說我沒吃那麼多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.59,0:28:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是今天不想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.63,0:29:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 讓宮姐用葡萄做點心不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.97,0:29:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.14,0:29:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.81,0:29:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,點心的話花也能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.27,0:29:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.23,0:29:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 做嘛做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.36,0:29:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是會給人家添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.95,0:29:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧 外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.08,0:29:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當然可以 廚房隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.41,0:29:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.79,0:29:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,葡萄甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.67,0:29:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.05,0:29:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,趁這個機會大家一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.01,0:29:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.47,0:29:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.01,0:29:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起 聽起來很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.10,0:29:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 低筋麵粉在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.35,0:29:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,低筋麵粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.94,0:29:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我想做葡萄撻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.02,0:29:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.98,0:30:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天您做的點心裡有撻 所以我想應該有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.20,0:30:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,材料 低筋麵粉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.70,0:30:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 就是那個 我放哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.67,0:30:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不剩多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,夠用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.30,0:30:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有點少
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.34,0:30:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就沒有點心吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.17,0:30:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.89,0:30:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.81,0:30:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明膠
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.43,0:30:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,葡萄果凍怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.98,0:30:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.48,0:30:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,涼涼的甜點也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.81,0:30:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 果凍也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.11,0:30:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我準備做果凍 請妳們幫忙把葡萄剝皮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.32,0:30:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.86,0:30:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來 大家一起來剝皮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.87,0:30:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.41,0:30:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐 這個要全剝掉也太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.17,0:30:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,燙過再剝比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.75,0:30:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,像番茄那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.55,0:31:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.80,0:31:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.47,0:31:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 這麼簡單啊 一下就剝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.06,0:31:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還有生奶油嗎 有的話我想用作裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.77,0:31:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,生奶油啊 我放哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.69,0:31:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.32,0:31:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.54,0:31:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 這樣舔不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.55,0:31:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆也這麼手笨
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.46,0:31:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.93,0:31:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.01,0:31:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 其實白天的點心和晚飯都不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.60,0:32:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,果然啊 外婆不擅長下廚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.07,0:32:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.11,0:32:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩的時候總是媽媽做 或者是町婆婆來做
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以剛才町婆婆來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.12,0:32:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽春香介紹了宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.58,0:32:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說宮子特別擅長做點心 和花還特別要好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.71,0:32:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然後為什麼說謊？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.80,0:32:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我就感覺花被宮子搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.43,0:32:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想妳有了這麼好的朋友 以後就不會來外婆家玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.02,0:32:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我這外婆真是丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.15,0:32:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼丟人的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.07,0:32:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡外婆了 也很高興帶大家過來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.53,0:32:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還有 以後我也會經常來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.83,0:32:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.00,0:33:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要像宮子一樣學會做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.46,0:33:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.76,0:33:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.01,0:33:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和花一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.85,0:33:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,凍好之前妳們先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,極樂極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.61,0:33:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,極樂？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.19,0:33:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.20,0:33:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.28,0:33:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 閨蜜會是樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.37,0:33:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這地方真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.79,0:33:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了春香 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.67,0:33:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用謝 聽到小花主動說想和大家一起旅行 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.47,0:33:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她還是第一次提出這種請求 我特別想讓她去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.68,0:33:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我家也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.39,0:34:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,宮子竟然會說自己也想去 我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.77,0:34:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她最近好像過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.65,0:34:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐是個好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.40,0:34:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她和小花一直要好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.86,0:34:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們和我們都一直要好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.28,0:34:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.70,0:34:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.79,0:34:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.71,0:34:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.88,0:34:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛她們現在也在洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.64,0:34:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還是第一次五個人一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.60,0:34:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.39,0:34:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.81,0:34:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 再暖和一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.90,0:34:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.66,0:34:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,花 妳外婆真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.91,0:35:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.37,0:35:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有時候聽不懂話 但是很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.50,0:35:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她為了讓妳看到能幹的一面而努力 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.21,0:35:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她真是喜歡小花
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.92,0:35:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和宮姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.18,0:35:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我還說飯是自己做的 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.02,0:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我也做過類似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.69,0:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.07,0:35:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但是我撐不住 馬上就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.03,0:35:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候真是羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.37,0:35:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.17,0:35:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 您戴的髮夾和小花的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.00,0:35:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這是小時候町姐姐送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.13,0:35:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您的那位朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.81,0:36:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我非常珍貴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.40,0:36:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真羨慕 能有這麼棒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.91,0:36:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就沒有這麼要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.12,0:36:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,花和妳看起來非常要好 難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.21,0:36:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是花和我年齡相差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.63,0:36:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,交朋友和年齡沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.59,0:36:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.76,0:36:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,日向真是的 像個小孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.03,0:36:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是小孩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.49,0:37:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.20,0:37:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.53,0:37:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.87,0:37:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上明明起那麼早 她們真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.54,0:37:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.88,0:37:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候來這裡住的時候標記過身高
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.67,0:37:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.97,0:37:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點不想讓妳知道以前的身高 感覺會被濫用
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.31,0:37:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.81,0:37:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事情日後會變成美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.73,0:37:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不光是對本人 對於家人朋友 以及當時在一起的人也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.36,0:37:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,由妳來說就沒多少說服力了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.78,0:37:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.20,0:37:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.45,0:37:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個我來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.00,0:37:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:37:59.59,Default,,400,0,0,,那睡覺的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.17,0:38:00.17,Default,,0,400,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.97,0:38:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.68,0:38:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天的主要活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.68,0:38:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,主要活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.64,0:38:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.85,0:38:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.81,0:38:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,枕頭大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.44,0:38:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說是修學旅行必有的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.19,0:38:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.78,0:38:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 來打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.70,0:38:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 日向 住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.20,0:38:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.66,0:38:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.17,0:38:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.93,0:38:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.94,0:38:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.69,0:38:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.17,0:39:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.25,0:39:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.63,0:39:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.22,0:39:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.34,0:39:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因為今天有祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.85,0:39:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.68,0:39:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,點燈的船還有燈籠之類的順流而下很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.15,0:39:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有船啊 感覺很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.36,0:39:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妳看過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.15,0:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要去祭典的話 今天的計劃要改一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.07,0:39:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.41,0:39:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.87,0:39:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.21,0:39:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是鬍子哥
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.67,0:39:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以前沒有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.34,0:40:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 穿上這個拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 請給我拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.89,0:40:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.31,0:40:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意 纜車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.15,0:40:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.95,0:40:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好美的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.95,0:40:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.88,0:40:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來 我們從這裡走著去動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.97,0:40:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,距離還挺遠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.14,0:40:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.30,0:40:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.64,0:40:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.89,0:41:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 會摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.40,0:41:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.07,0:41:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,走了好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.41,0:41:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.91,0:41:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好大的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.71,0:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是豚鼠 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.17,0:41:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,早上很早起來 已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.59,0:41:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 那邊有猴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.59,0:41:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡等著 妳去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.51,0:41:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 宮姐不看猴嗎 那可是猴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.10,0:41:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,猴…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.10,0:41:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐姐睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.73,0:41:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她累了 讓她睡一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.19,0:41:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.44,0:41:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不看猴了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.28,0:41:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也累了 在這裡等著 妳們去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.15,0:41:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小花不看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.07,0:41:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前來過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.87,0:41:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能放下宮姐不管
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.74,0:41:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有我看著她 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.25,0:42:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,日向走吧 猴子在等著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.46,0:42:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.92,0:42:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.87,0:42:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是猴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.29,0:42:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.12,0:42:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 那邊在賣餌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.67,0:42:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我來餵
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.04,0:42:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想餵食
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來餵食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.42,0:42:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要多吃 快快長大
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.39,0:42:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是猴王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.22,0:42:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是夫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.40,0:43:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起小花
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.61,0:43:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.19,0:43:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 日向她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.03,0:43:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去看猴子了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.99,0:43:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不去沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.12,0:43:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前來過
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.29,0:43:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.66,0:43:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.33,0:43:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可能因為睡了一會兒吧 我有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.50,0:43:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.05,0:43:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妳明明不喜歡旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.76,0:43:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的確幾乎沒有去旅行過 但我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.06,0:43:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很開心 來了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.69,0:43:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.94,0:43:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.36,0:43:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看到猴了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.91,0:44:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 妳高興就好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.87,0:44:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 宮姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.66,0:44:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.83,0:44:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.62,0:44:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纜車要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.54,0:44:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 回去之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.09,0:44:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.72,0:44:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,難得去一次祭典 我就從鄰居那裡借來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.64,0:44:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們最可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.14,0:44:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是 大家都很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.23,0:44:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很適合妳
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.78,0:44:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 宮姐也很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.28,0:44:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.20,0:44:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.79,0:44:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.46,0:44:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來 穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.79,0:44:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.21,0:44:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.09,0:45:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 冰淇淋看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.60,0:45:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.77,0:45:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.86,0:45:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小依說了等下要吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.49,0:45:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.78,0:45:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 長瀞布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.83,0:45:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.37,0:45:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要嚐嚐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.62,0:45:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.33,0:45:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我經常吃 所以想讓姐姐嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.51,0:45:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就嚐嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.72,0:45:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是我想吃而已
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.64,0:45:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.35,0:45:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,布…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.77,0:45:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要兩個布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.35,0:45:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 終於到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.98,0:45:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊有很多紀念品店
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.57,0:46:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.07,0:46:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我想去這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.24,0:46:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.03,0:46:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,射擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.33,0:46:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.08,0:46:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夏季祭典上是妳幫我拿的獎品 今天我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.50,0:46:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.34,0:46:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.42,0:46:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.88,0:46:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.97,0:46:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音 妳有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.23,0:46:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.60,0:46:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真有眼光 那是最受歡迎的獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.06,0:46:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.32,0:46:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.15,0:46:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.82,0:46:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,子彈有五發 記得要擊落
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.91,0:46:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.50,0:46:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.22,0:47:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一發
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.64,0:47:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.35,0:47:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會拿到它
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.88,0:47:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的冰是天然冰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.34,0:47:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.84,0:47:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,花從以前就喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.14,0:47:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.64,0:47:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.18,0:47:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也吃我的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.10,0:47:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,夏音的也好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.23,0:48:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 現在是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.57,0:48:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,日向的看起來也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.24,0:48:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.41,0:48:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,來了真是太好了 夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.83,0:48:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.80,0:48:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看 好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.80,0:48:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.05,0:48:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.35,0:48:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是船
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.48,0:48:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.65,0:48:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看 乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.37,0:48:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.33,0:48:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,每年都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.08,0:49:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多人遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.92,0:49:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.29,0:49:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不要離我太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.01,0:49:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.26,0:49:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.26,0:49:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人這麼多的話 感覺松本也會混在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.56,0:49:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,松本啊 是啊 可能在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.10,0:49:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 我都沒告訴她會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.15,0:49:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 怎麼說也不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.49,0:49:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 我們去吃棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.53,0:49:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.88,0:49:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,腳疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.34,0:49:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不疼 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.57,0:50:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.24,0:50:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.56,0:50:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.56,0:50:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.44,0:50:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 小花 妳的髮夾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.77,0:50:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.48,0:50:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是掉在什麼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.45,0:50:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.32,0:50:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跑 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.95,0:50:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去找
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.66,0:50:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,乃愛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.62,0:51:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也去找
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.56,0:51:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,髮卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.06,0:51:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.31,0:51:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人送來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.98,0:51:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.90,0:51:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.02,0:51:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.98,0:51:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.57,0:51:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,掉在哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們再找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.49,0:51:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還有沒找的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.07,0:51:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.08,0:51:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,花 我會再給妳做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.33,0:51:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我再找一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.96,0:51:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐找的話我也找
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.05,0:51:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也找
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.93,0:51:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當然也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.22,0:51:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 夏音
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.14,0:52:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,天已經黑了 妳們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.81,0:52:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託您照顧大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.64,0:52:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.10,0:52:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是宮姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.52,0:52:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的 乖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.74,0:52:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.74,0:52:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.04,0:52:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.16,0:52:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐交給我吧 我不會迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.58,0:52:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.30,0:52:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妳要小心 花
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.46,0:52:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來 我們回家等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.84,0:52:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.71,0:54:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她們一定快回來了 我們去裡面等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.09,0:54:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.51,0:54:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.93,0:54:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,費了好大工夫才攔住日向
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.43,0:54:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.52,0:54:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.10,0:54:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我好擔心宮姐和花
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.48,0:54:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.06,0:54:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.24,0:55:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒妳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.86,0:55:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.41,0:55:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,髮卡找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.24,0:55:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐幫我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.95,0:55:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了 花
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.79,0:55:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,宮子 真是謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.34,0:55:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不用謝 但是煙花大會結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.05,0:55:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,煙花的話這裡有
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.01,0:55:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.84,0:55:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,町婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.76,0:55:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 各位 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.68,0:55:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.06,0:55:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,來 大家都進來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.44,0:55:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,點著了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這顏色好看
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.53,0:55:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小櫻 葡萄要不要來一粒？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.07,0:55:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我昨天也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.49,0:55:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.74,0:55:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的冷笑話都傳染給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.04,0:55:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 是妳傳染給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.25,0:55:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.83,0:56:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.04,0:56:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都說是妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.59,0:56:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.72,0:56:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 畢竟相處這麼長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.72,0:56:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.94,0:56:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小花交到了一個好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.57,0:56:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來玩哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.66,0:56:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.03,0:56:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 鬧鬼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.04,0:56:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.62,0:56:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.87,0:56:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是青蛙？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.46,0:56:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去看
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.92,0:56:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.17,0:56:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小依 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.34,0:56:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的布丁很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.97,0:56:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,妳從以前就喜歡甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.06,0:56:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 妳去下面的池塘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.02,0:56:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.77,0:57:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到好東西 我們去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.94,0:57:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小花 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.49,0:57:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒問題 馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.37,0:57:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很黑 妳要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.54,0:57:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人反而讓我放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.18,0:57:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 那個 謝謝妳幫我找到髮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.35,0:57:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不用謝 找到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.15,0:57:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是外婆送妳的珍貴髮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.57,0:57:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.57,0:57:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要回去了啊 要是能這樣一直和妳在一起該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.24,0:58:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在胡說什麼呢 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.62,0:58:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,變成老婆婆也一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.67,0:58:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,希望妳也能交到這樣的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.97,0:58:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 我之前送妳的髮夾 妳不戴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.47,0:58:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想弄丟 所以收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.14,0:58:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不戴豈不是沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.56,0:58:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.36,0:58:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳那麼珍惜它就好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.19,0:58:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.15,0:58:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.45,0:58:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不戴上髮卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.95,0:58:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.12,0:58:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以幫我戴上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.97,0:58:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.49,0:59:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.37,0:59:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.54,0:59:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.25,0:59:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是螢火蟲 還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.25,0:59:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.54,0:59:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們兩個說了什麼悄悄話？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.88,0:59:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.96,0:59:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們看螢火蟲來著
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.38,0:59:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.94,0:59:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.07,0:59:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.15,0:59:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.87,0:59:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.74,1:00:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.79,1:00:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.58,1:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高興 妳們以後再來玩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.00,1:00:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.88,1:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去祭典了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.55,1:00:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,每年都很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.97,1:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.43,1:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,練習旅行非常成功
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.10,1:00:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是到家之前都是練習旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.39,1:00:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回去路上要小心
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.68,1:00:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.69,1:00:29.69,Upper,,0,0,0,,不想回家啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.27,1:00:32.69,Upper,,0,0,0,,下次還有修學旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.10,1:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,花 妳能交到這麼好的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.69,1:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宮姐也去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.11,1:00:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我去不了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.82,1:00:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那下次再來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.25,1:00:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,町姐姐 我們變成老婆婆也繼續做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.80,1:00:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 變成老婆婆也要在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.20,1:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,宮子同學 玩得好開心啊
